{"tid":852631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戀上東主後情變 雙程證工場女亮利剪架頸對峙","createTime":"2018-10-08T03:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T04:26:11.000Z","uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de09ef0925ea3ade7f62929cd3aad716afd7d351","tid":852631,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"火炭黃竹洋街5號富昌中心一食品工場，凌晨1時許，一名32歲任兼職女員工，據悉，因感情問題與姓戴(55歲)食品工場東主爭執後，激動拿起一柄利剪揮舞，在場另一名男職員見狀，立刻逃出工場及報警，東主則退入另一房間並反鎖，兩人對峙。消防員到場張開救生氣墊。<br />\n<br />\n警方新界南衝鋒隊第四隊何毅敬高級督察表示，談判專家隔門進行遊說，約一個多小時後，對峙女子情緒激動爬上窗花，並打開窗戶企圖跳樓，情況危急，在別無選擇下衝鋒隊警員立刻用工具破門進入工場內，上前及時將女子拉回安全地方，她稍後由救護員送院治理。據悉，女事主持雙程證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181008/58768745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58768745&d=GnYOVBWD5ThRqoI9%2BJHumS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b2ab8e81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58768745&h=57b7a2c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181008/58768745</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫雞叫出事.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f72a61453c2ca68c477afc940aa269cf0e5074","tid":852631,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"真係傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a5a30d2f4522e7410aaac9f70bbf4fc6612262","tid":852631,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"相？"},{"pid":"44827a7b2f257b0638033959b119939c233fe5cd","tid":852631,"uid":189243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"揸雙程證嚟香港兼職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}